{"tid":2495190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳靜1,528萬沽荃灣地鐵上蓋單位    Dada持貨4年賺逾303萬：我一直睇好樓市前景","createTime":"2021-04-19T04:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:26:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d10d0bc7f4b6109fbde77c884c2c477dbd706cad","tid":2495190,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2f49ec/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_201226/20201226_4133c1fdf1632bdb3534YjbpKfXrdB3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F2f49ec%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_201226%2F20201226_4133c1fdf1632bdb3534YjbpKfXrdB3r.jpg&h=ef965af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期二手樓市交投熾熱，不少藝人都有出售自己物業，他們多數都是賺住賣。近日藝人陳靜（Dada）就將她在荃灣海之戀單位出售，位於7座中低層。陳靜出售的單位為西鐵站上蓋，所以都是熱門樓盤，最後成功售出，勁賺25％。<br />\n<br />\n陳靜持有的荃灣海之戀7座中低層單位一出將單位作出租用途，而租客快將搬走，所以就出售。單位最後以1,528萬港元沽出，呎價約19,665元。該單位實用面積777方呎，三房間隔，近月一度叫價1,568萬元放售。<br />\n<br />\nDada的單位買入近4年，現時帳面賺約303.2萬元，升值約25%。陳靜承認出售以上物業後表示，見到價錢適合就售出，而且一直睇好樓市前景。"},{"pid":"699d6a3c4e8acbaa5eebc0bbc941bb565ffe718b","tid":2495190,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"而且一直睇好樓市前景。<br />\n<br />\n睇好又賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔等升多一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排賺夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4731e7376cd2622d3f67231c7f3a1a5c90acca2","tid":2495190,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"4年賺25%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nspy 4年都double<br />\n睇好又唔SH?"},{"pid":"d85f0ff5e1adbed71048f454bd40da233167875c","tid":2495190,"uid":33730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"幾年前都要千二萬，當年買樓嗰舊錢點嚟<